I am in Indiana and I am one of those people that have no use for people that are fake. I am not necessarily what you would call a fan because the only people I am fans of are ones who affect me personally but I admire your effort to do what you have accomplished. I see people for what they are. You, like the rest of us, are nowhere near perfect, but you deserved a great deal more than what this twit gave you.

I will be one of those that defend you because what I know of you and what I know of her tells me all I need to know. I wish I could do something to make it easier for you but of course there is not. If you ever decide that you need a cup of coffee and some adult conversation and support, I'll be here.

From the years I have been entertained by you, I have seen nothing to give me any reason not to believe you. You put your children first and that by himself gives me reason to support you.
